- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the human-machine interface and the driver's trust in the automation system. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses driving automation systems. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses the levels of driving automation systems and their functions. 
- cs.HCI (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category as the paper discusses the driver's behavior and perception in relation to the automation system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the sophistication of the automation system's functions.
